song_name: Smile When I See You Smile My Love

version_description: Complete chord sheet including key changes / intermediate with split chords and suggestions for playable voicings.
I lowered the key to E from F# to make it easier to sing. In the bridge, there's an underlying progression of (E Dm A E) over the E that's noted but it's not necessary, I suppose.
Full version of this song that can be played electric or acoustic.
The other version all have wrong chords I've put the correct chords and corrected the intro, solo and ending.
